member.name: T:Nevron.Nov.Examples.Diagram.NGraphTemplate
member.summary: The NGraphTemplate class is a template, which serves as base class for all templates which create graph
member.remarks:
It enhances its base with the following features:
Vertex style and Edge style attributes Exposed by the VerticesUserClass and EdgesUserClass properties
Control over the vertices shape and size Exposed by the VerticesSize and VerticesShape properties
Generic spacing control Exposed by the HorizontalSpacing and VerticalSpacing properties
Ability to create new vertices and edges which conform to the template settings
Achieved with the help of the CreateLineGraphEdge and CreateGraphVertex methods.
